"{\"uid\": \"walesonline.co.uk-lifestyle-tv-gmbs-kate-garraway-corrected-olympic-29707191\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Josh Kerr, the athlete who clinched a silver medal in the Men's 1500m at the Paris Olympics, appeared onGood Morning Britainon Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9212968925223285, \"rank\": 0.03365066462179148, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite narrowly missing out on gold, Josh improved upon his previous bronze medal achievement.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9212968925223285, \"rank\": 0.03365066462179148, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During his video link interview with hosts Kate Garraway and Rob Rinder, he discussed his Olympic experience.\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Garraway\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Garraway\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Garraway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Garraway\"}, {\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Rinder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rob Rinder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Rinder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Rinder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, when Kate mentioned she'd heard that Josh prefers not to have his family at races due to the added pressure, he was quick to set the record straight.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999977009686136, \"rank\": 2.299084163773078e-05, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9212968925223285, \"rank\": 0.03365066462179148, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kate asked, \\\"I know you generally - well you have been reported as saying this, you might tell me different - you generally are not sure about having your mum and dad there when you race as it almost throws you a little bit.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999977009686136, \"rank\": 2.299084163773078e-05, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know they are supporting you but it puts an extra pressure.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were there (in Paris) and I believe you did not know they were there until afterwards.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989731805, \"rank\": 1.0268563957793008e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"